column3: He's young, he's stylish, and he knows all the moves! The soul of the party and the king of the dance floor─Dancing Green!
The ring is her studio, and reality her canvas! She's the rebel with a cause who captivates all with her illusions─Sugar Riot!
He's back for revenge─with a vengeance! The despicable fighter formerly known as the Brute Bomber─the Brute Abombinator!
With his peerless bladework and preternatural agility, he's the apex predator of the cruiserweight division─the Howling Blade!
The match is decided! Victory goes to the challenger!
